snippet: Buddy Hield scored 22 points and Ryan Spangler added 16 points and a career-high 15 rebounds to help Oklahoma knock off previously unbeaten Iowa State 87-82 Saturday....

headline.print_headline: Hield, Spangler Lead Oklahoma Past No. 9 Iowa St.
